ai-kv5.10:1.1_0: the knowledge of the fruit of his disciples,
ai-kv5.10:1.3_0: and the disciple of their disciples?
ai-kv5.10:2.1_0: the knowledge of the fruit of his disciples,
ai-kv5.10:2.3_0: Is there a disciple of a disciple of the faculties, a disciple of individuals, and a trainee.
ai-kv5.10:3.1_0: the knowledge of the fruit of his disciples,
ai-kv5.10:3.3_0: There is what is known as the aggregates, terminology, and description of the sense faculties.
ai-kv5.10:4.1_0: the knowledge of the fruit of his disciples,
ai-kv5.10:4.3_0: and a disciple of the teacher, the disciple who is a all-knowing and all-seeing, to know and see, the teaching, and the Dhamma?”
ai-kv5.10:5.1_0: the knowledge of the fruit of his disciples,
ai-kv5.10:5.3_0: They give rise to the unarisen path, gave birth to the unborn path, explained the unexplained path. They know the path, understand the path, and are expert on the path.
ai-kv5.10:6.1_0: should not correct them like this:
ai-kv5.10:6.2_0: “Which knowledge has the fruits of crystal?”
ai-kv5.10:6.6_0: he knows the meaning of fruit of his disciples.
ai-kv5.10:6.7_0: The story of the fruits of knowledge is finished.
ai-kv5.10:7.1_0: He knows the knowledge of freedom, the knowledge and vision of freedom. ... the knowledge and vision of freedom.
ai-kv5.10:8.1_0: The layman Upasena, Vaṅga, Upatissa, and the power of freedom.’
